claim: John F. Kennedy was killed in a military invasion.
premise_source_doc_sentence: The Bay of Pigs Invasion  (  Spanish : Invasión de Playa Girón or Invasión de Bahía de Cochinos or Batalla de Girón  )  was a failed military invasion of Cuba undertaken by the CIA-sponsored paramilitary group Brigade 2506 on 17 April 1961 .
